<li><i>The trial of Bernhard Goetz</i> (ASIN B0006DAN94).</li>
<li><i>People Vs. Goetz: The Summations and the Charges to the Jury</i> (<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0899416578" class="internal">ISBN 0-89941-657-8</a>).</li>
<li><a href="http://select.nytimes.com/search/restricted/article?res=FB0614FD3A5C0C768EDDAB0994DC484D81" class="external text" title="http://select.nytimes.com/search/restricted/article?res=FB0614FD3A5C0C768EDDAB0994DC484D81" rel="nofollow">"CALLERS SUPPORT SUBWAY GUNMAN" (early news of incident, NY Times subscription required)</a></li>
<li><a href="http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F01E0DC1639F935A15757C0A960958260" class="external text" title="http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F01E0DC1639F935A15757C0A960958260" rel="nofollow">New York Times sets the record straight</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.bookrags.com/biography/bernhard-hugo-goetz-cri/" class="external text" title="http://www.bookrags.com/biography/bernhard-hugo-goetz-cri/" rel="nofollow"><i>BookRags</i> (interesting old summary of case)</a></li>
</ul>
